    <dataqual>
        <posacc>
            <horizpa>
                <horizpar>Registered to tax lots. Street center lines were digitized from aerial orthophotography at +/- 10 feet accuracy. Tax lots were fit to the street centerlines. Beaverton, Oregon City and Tigard planning areas were improved to +/- 5 feet accuracy. Multnomah County was created with coordinate geometry using better control.</horizpar>
            </horizpa>
        </posacc>
        <lineage>
            <procstep>
                <procdesc>The precincts file was updated with data from the three counties. If any further updates are available before the November election, they will be posted on the DRC ftp site.</procdesc>
                <procdate>200007</procdate>
            </procstep>
            <procstep>
                <procdesc>Projection information (.prj file), compatible with ArcGIS 8.1, was added to the layer.</procdesc>
                <procdate>20010715</procdate>
            </procstep>
            <procstep>
                <procdesc>Incorporated 2006 precincts from Multnomah County.</procdesc>
                <procdate>20060811</procdate>
            </procstep>
            <procstep>
                <procdesc>Updated boundaries based on data provided by our data partners.  Data now maintained as a geodatabase in SDE.</procdesc>
                <procdate>20081103</procdate>
            </procstep>
            <procstep>
                <procdesc>Voter Precincts following the boundary between the states of Oregon and Washington were updated to precise state boundary line coordinates. The boundary between Oregon and Washington is defined by ORS 186.520 which lists latitude and longitude coordinate stations connected by a series of straight lines along length of the boundary.</procdesc>
                <procdate>20120423</procdate>
            </procstep>
            <procstep>
                <procdesc>Major edits to Washington County and minor edits to Clackamas County, reflective of precincts for upcoming November election.</procdesc>
                <procdate>20161102</procdate>
            </procstep>
            <procstep>
                <procdesc>Major edits to Multnomah County; minor edits to Washington and Clackamas Counties. Reflective of precincts for upcoming November election.</procdesc>
                <procdate>20181018</procdate>
            </procstep>
            <procstep>
                <procdesc>Correction to Multnomah County boundaries. Previous release used an older version of precinct data in Multnomah County.</procdesc>
                <procdate>20181211</procdate>
            </procstep>
            <procstep>
